title: Passenger who took 2021 trip to see Titanic says missing sub 'was not safe'
description: A man who visited the Titanic wreck on the missing sub two years ago has said he felt the small vessel "was not safe".

title: UK would back fast-track for Ukraine to join NATO, foreign secretary says
description: The UK would back a fast-track for Ukraine to join NATO, the foreign secretary has signalled.

title: 'We don't know what they are': Search for origin of 'noises' will continue in sub hunt, Coast Guard says
description: It is unclear what some noises heard near the wreck of the Titanic actually are, the US Coast Guard has said.

title: Seven people 'critical' after explosion in Paris sparks fire and reduces buildings to rubble
description: Seven people are in a critical condition and nine more are injured after a large explosion in the Latin Quarter of central Paris, police have said.

title: Mourinho banned for four UEFA games after abusing English referee Anthony Taylor
description: Jose Mourinho has been banned for four UEFA matches after abusing referee Anthony Taylor at the Europa League final.

title: French submersible robot with remote-controlled arms to join Titan search
description: A French robot that can dive to a depth of 6,000 metres is due to arrive in the North Atlantic late on Wednesday and join the search for the missing submersible, Titan.

title: Rishi Sunak is taking same 'militaristic line' as Boris Johnson, Russian ambassador to UK warns
description: Rishi Sunak is taking the same "militaristic line" as Boris Johnson and should be doing more to help bring about peace talks between Moscow and Kyiv, Russia's ambassador to the UK has told Sky News.

title: Major search continues for missing sub as half the rescue boats still on way
description: Of the 10 vessels involved in the hunt for the missing submersible Titan, five are now at the search site but four others listed by the US Coast Guard won't get there today, according to marine tracking data.

title: Long-lost sisters separated for 60 years united after surprising DNA test
description: Two sisters who had no idea the other existed have been united after spending more than 60 years apart, thanks to a surprising DNA test.

title: Sister and aunt of missing passengers says 'sole focus' is rescue of 'beloved' family members
description: A sister and aunt of two passengers on board the missing Titan submersible has said the family's "sole focus" is their rescue.

title: Underwater noises in search for the Titan - are they a sign of life and what does it mean for the search?
description: Underwater noises heard during the frantic search for the submersible Titan have sparked fresh hopes of finding the missing vessel  - but what do experts think?

title: Explorers make 'monumental' ancient city discovery in southern Mexico jungle
description: An ancient Mayan city thought to date back to 1,000AD has been unearthed in southern Mexico.

title: A tsunami of filth as sewage and sludge coat streets of Kherson after dam blast
description: As the waters go down here, the full extent of the damage is becoming clear.

title: Biden's description of Xi Jinping as 'dictator' criticised as 'absurd and irresponsible'
description: China says comments by Joe Biden describing its leader Xi Jinping as a dictator are "extremely absurd and irresponsible".

title: Four people shot dead by gunmen at West Bank service station
description: Four Israelis have been shot dead and another four injured by Palestinian gunmen at a service station in the occupied West Bank.

title: A billionaire, one of Pakistan's richest men and 'Mr Titanic': Who is on missing submersible?
description: The search is continuing to find the submersible that lost contact near the wreck of the Titanic.

title: Andrew Tate and brother arrive at court over human trafficking allegations
description: Controversial influencer Andrew Tate and his brother Tristan have arrived at a Romanian court after being charged over allegations of human trafficking and forming an organised crime group.

title: 'Serious safety concerns' over Titan submersible had been 'met with hostility'
description: A former employee of the missing Titan submersible operator has revealed he had raised "safety concerns" over the vessel but was reportedly "met with hostility" before later being sacked, court documents have shown.

title: 'This is how it is going to end' - Scientist recounts trapped Titanic submersible experience
description: A scientist who visited the Titanic in 2000 and was caught in a strong underwater current at the site says he thought he would die in the submersible.
